cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is about text classification, which falls under the natural language processing (NLP) domain. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a novel approach using meta-learning and dynamic routing algorithm, which involves machine learning techniques, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper discusses the effectiveness of the proposed approach in handling unseen classes, which relates to the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed approach also involves learning a generalized representation of each class, which could be related to computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE).
